                <p>
                    <lb n="1"/><g type="pc"/> cālivākaṉa-cakā<orig>pi</orig>ttam <num value="1775"><g type="numeral">1000</g>
                    <lb n="2"/>7 <g type="numeral">100</g> 7 <g type="numeral">10</g> 5</num> kaliyukā<orig>pi</orig>ttam <num value="4885">4 <g type="numeral">1000</g> 8
                    <lb n="3" break="no"/><g type="numeral">100</g> 8 <g type="numeral">10</g> 4</num> Itaṉ m<choice><sic>e</sic><corr>ē</corr></choice>l cellā niṉṟa
                    <lb n="4"/>cōpakiṟutu <g type="varuṣam"/> Āvaṇi <g type="mācam"/> <num value="30">3 <g type="numeral">10</g></num> <g type="tēti"/>
