                    <lb n="6" break="no"/><supplied reason="omitted">t</supplied>tiramuṅ kūṭiṉa cupatiṉat=til
                </p>
                <p>
                    māci
                    <lb n="7" break="no"/>lāmaṇi-y-īcuvara-cuvāmi caṉṉati tu
                    <lb n="8" break="no"/>ca-k=-kampamum taḷavicaiyu=M cēṉai
                    <lb n="9" break="no"/>-k-kuṭai cuppiṟamaṇiya-ce<unclear reason="eccentric_ductus">ṭṭi</unclear>yār
                    <lb n="10"/>kumāraṉ Āpatuttāraṇa-ceṭṭi
                    <lb n="11" break="no"/>yār ce<choice><orig>yi</orig><reg>y</reg></choice>tu vaitta taṟmam
                </p>
                <p>
                    nitti
                    <lb n="12" break="no"/>yam catāc<choice><sic>e</sic><corr>ē</corr></choice>ṟvai <g type="pc">.</g> 
